org.spdx.spdxspreadsheet

Class LicenseSheet

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.spdx.spdxspreadsheet.AbstractSheet
      • org.spdx.spdxspreadsheet.LicenseSheet

  • public class LicenseSheet
extends AbstractSheet
    Spreadsheet holding SPDX Licenses The text column can contain either the text for the license or a hyperlink to a file containing the text. The text file location is relative to the directory containing the spreadsheet.
    Author:
    Gary O'Neall
